LabDelivery

Agent Nurse
Agent LabPersonnel
Agent Transporter
Agent Arm
Location patientFloor
Location laboratory
Resource sample

Nurse:
	1: fetch sample
	2: stop

LabPersonnel:
	1: stop

Transporter:
	1: moveTo patientFloor
	2: receiveFrom Nurse
	3: moveTo laboratory
	4: stop

Arm:
	1-3: stop
	4: receiveFrom Transporter
	5: deliver sample

success: !possess(Transporter, sample)
failure: time(20)